" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755219"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Puh – da muss ich überlegen. Das ist eine gute Frage.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1803" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1812" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755226"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Von 2000 bis 2003.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1813" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1818" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755230"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Dann bin ich ausgestiegen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1827" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1838" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755240"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, das ist lange her!</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1839" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1854" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755242"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>#Name3 war auch der Vorsitzende, bis er gestorben ist, stimmt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1873" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1894" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755272"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>#Name2 war dabei und #Name1.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1895" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1899" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755274"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Diese Gruppe von Leuten.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1901" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1914" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755283"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Genau, er war auch groß, richtig? Das waren die Leute, die damals dabei waren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1922" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1930" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755289"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, stimmt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1935" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1938" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755292"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>So sah es aus.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1945" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755295"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Läuft es noch?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2083" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2090" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755365"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Heute ist alles ja anders.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2090" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2101" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755367"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sie sind viel unterwegs z.B. in Discos usw.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2101" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2110" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755372"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Die Zeit damals war anders.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2110" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2113" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755377"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Der Fokus lag auf dem Sport.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2113" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2120" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755384"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Heute hat man keine Zeit mehr dafür.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2121" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2124" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755387"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Na ja, das ist komisch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2154" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2165" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755497"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Empor aus dem Osten und der Verein Comet wurden verbunden.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2165" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2171" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755500"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Später fand die Trennung statt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2171" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2180" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755502"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ach nein, zusammen mit dem B-G-S-V.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2180" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2197" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755509"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Comet blieb schon immer eigenständig und ist heute noch getrennt von anderen Vereinen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2203" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2212" ANNOTATION_ID="a2857585"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Stimmt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2266" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2284" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755539"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich denke, dass der Nachwuchs heute nicht mehr das Niveau erreicht wie „die Alten“ früher.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2284" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2297" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755550"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Jung und Alt sind auch nur noch selten zusammen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2354" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2363" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755591"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, Marco kenne ich auch.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2376" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2381" ANNOTATION_ID="a2867739"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das warst du, ach.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2397" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2411" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755607"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Er wollte mich auch für das Wasserballtraining holen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2411" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2427" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755612"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich hatte aber keine Zeit. Ich hatte eine eigene Familie. Das hat er auch verstanden.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2427" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2440" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755613"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Als Single hätte ich mitgemacht und die Einladung angenommen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2440" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2451" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755616"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Jemand meint auch, dass Wasserball gut für meine Figur wäre.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2451" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2468" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755618"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Am Anfang habe ich nur beim Training mitgemacht, ohne an Wettkämpfen teilzunehmen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2468" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2479" ANNOTATION_ID="a2755625"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Irgendwann war ich dann reif für die Mannschaft.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2479" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2484" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766842"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Jedoch habe ich es nicht geschafft, hinzukommen.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2485" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2504" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766848"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Eigentlich sollte ich im letzten Jahr dabei sein aber ich hatte keine Zeit.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2576" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2591" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766905"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Fußballvereine gibt es noch ein paar mehr.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2595" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2603" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766914"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, da gibt es viele Vereine überall in Deutschland verteilt.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2648" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2665" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766954"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Für mich sind Gesundheit und Sport wichtige Bereiche. Besser als keinen Sport zu treiben.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2703" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2713" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766964"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ja, bei mir ist das auch so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2713" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2742" ANNOTATION_ID="a2766975"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Ich bin viel mit meinen Kindern unterwegs. Wir besuchen unterschiedliche Verwandte. Wir wechseln uns untereinander immer ab.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2772" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2777" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767033"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Früher?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2782" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2788" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767040"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, wow.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2906" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2918" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767062"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wenn man nicht zufrieden ist, ist man oft krank geschrieben.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2918" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2933" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767063"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Bei einem Konflikt oder Streit meldet man sich dann krank.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2933" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2936" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767065"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Das machen die meisten so.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2936" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2955" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767068"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wenn man sich wohl fühlt, tut man es nicht.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2956" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2973" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767079"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wichtig ist, dass man auf sich selbst achtet. Was die anderen sagen, sollte einem egal sein.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2973" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2978" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767089"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Seinen eigenen Weg finden und gehen – darauf sollte man sich konzentrieren.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2979" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2988" ANNOTATION_ID="a2767094"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Sich nicht immer ducken und alles hinnehmen/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Translation_into_English_A" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_text__coarser_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-54"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1348" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1355" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895782"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, in Bulgaria, no sorry, Bucharest.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1723" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1727" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895326"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, well.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1743" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1758" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895328"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Back then I was part of the soccer club “Comet”.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1758" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1770" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895375"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Not anymore. I was on sick leave for a year because I had trouble with my knee.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1770" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1781" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895378"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Therefore I stopped doing sports and then I didn't have the time anymore.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1786" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1802" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895382"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh, I have to think about that for a second. That's a good question.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1803" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1812" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895386"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>From 2000 until 2003.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1813" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1818" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895387"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Then I left the club.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1827" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1838" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895391"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Wow, that was a long time ago.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1839" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1854" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895392"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>#Name3 was the first chairman until he died, right.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1873" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1894" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895396"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>#Name2 was there as well as #Name1.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1895" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1899" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895398"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>This group of people.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1901" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1914" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895402"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Exactly. Wasn't he really tall as well? They were the people who were there back then.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1922" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1930" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895406"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes. Right.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1935" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1938" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895407"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>That's what it looked like.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1939" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1945" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895409"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Is it going well?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2083" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2090" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895453"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, today everything changed.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2090" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2101" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895456"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They are out a lot, e.g. going clubbing and stuff like that.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2101" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2110" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895457"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>The time was just different.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2110" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2113" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895460"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Everything was focused on sports.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2113" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2120" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895462"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>There is no time for it nowadays.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2121" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2124" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895463"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Well, it's just odd.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2154" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2165" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895473"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>The Eastern club Empor and the club Comet merged.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2165" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2171" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895474"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>They separated again later.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2171" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2180" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895475"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>No sorry, together with the club B-G-S-V.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2180" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2197" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895476"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Comet was and always has been independent and still is, to this day, independent from other clubs.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2203" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2212" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895477"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Right.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2266" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2284" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895482"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I think the younger people today don't reach the same level as the “old hands” did in their time.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2284" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2297" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895483"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Young and old people aren't together quite as much.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2354" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2363" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895489"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, I know Marco, too.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2376" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2381" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895492"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>So that was you!</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2397" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2411" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895496"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>He wanted to recruit me for water polo, too.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2411" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2427" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895497"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I didn't have any time, though. I had a family. He understood that.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2427" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2440" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895498"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If had been single, I would have accepted his offer.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2440" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2451" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895500"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Somebody also said that water polo would benefit my figure.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2451" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2468" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895501"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>At first, I only joined the practices without participating in matches.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2468" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2479" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895502"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Some time passed and I was ready to join the team.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2479" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2484" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895503"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Though I didn't actually manage to go.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2485" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2504" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895504"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I was supposed to be on the team last year but I didn't have the time.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2576" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2591" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895509"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>There are a couple more soccer clubs left.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2595" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2603" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895512"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, there are many clubs all across Germany.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2648" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2665" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895515"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Health and sports are two very important topics for me. Better than not doing any sport at all.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2703" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2713" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895521"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Yes, I'm the same.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2713" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2742" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895522"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>I'm often away with my kids, then we go visit different family members. We always take turns visiting each other.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2772" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2777" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895523"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Used to be?</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2782" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2788" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895527"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Oh wow.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2906" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2918" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895540"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If one is dissatisfied, one is often on sick leave.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2918" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2933" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895544"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If there's a conflict or a fight, one often takes a sick leave.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2933" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2936" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895546"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>Many people do it that way.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2936" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2955" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895547"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>If you're feeling comfortable, you usually don't take a sick leave.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2956" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2973" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895550"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>What's important is that one takes care of oneself. It shouldn't matter what other people say.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2973" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2978" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895553"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>One should focus on finding one's own path.</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts2979" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts2988" ANNOTATION_ID="a2895556"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>One shouldn't just obey and accept everything/</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION></TIER><TIER TIER_ID="Lexem_Geb&#xE4;rde_r_A" LINGUISTIC_TYPE_REF="L_tokens_right_left__finer_granularity" PARTICIPANT="ber-54"><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1349" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1350" ANNOTATION_ID="a2283010_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>BULGARIEN1</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1352" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1354" ANNOTATION_ID="a2779199_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>$ALPHA1:B</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1746" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1748" ANNOTATION_ID="a2325854_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>FRÜHER1*</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1750" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1753" ANNOTATION_ID="a2325852_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>$NAME-COMET1</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1754" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts1755" ANNOTATION_ID="a2325848_1"><ANNOTATION_VALUE>FUSSBALL2</ANNOTATION_VALUE></ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION></ANNOTATION><ANNOTATION><ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts1756" TIME_SLOT_REF2